    "engine oil": "Toyota Europe\u2019s periodic maintenance schedule for Yaris lists maintenance points every 15,000 km (or 12 months for normal conditions), including engine oil and filter replacement\u2014see Toyota Europe warranty and maintenance documentation (e.g. toyota-tech.eu maintenance schedule PDFs for regional equivalents).",
